Game Codes Marketplace - Functional Requirements Document

Project Overview:
  A digital marketplace platform that allows customers to purchase game activation codes for various gaming platforms. 
  The system facilitates instant delivery of digital game codes to customers after successful payment.

Purpose:
  To provide gamers with a convenient, secure, and instant way to purchase game activation codes for popular gaming platforms at competitive prices.

Core Functions:
 - Browse and search available game codes
 - Purchase game codes securely
 - Receive instant code delivery
 - Manage user accounts and purchase history
 - Process payments
 - Manage inventory (admin)
